Subject: Setup post upgrade
Description: We have just upgraded our system to 11.6 and need some help getting a few things sorted out.  Our StealthAudit user website is down , and so is the AIC website. Our AD inventory scan fails after the upgrade as well.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issues]
- AIC is down
- Published Reports is down
- SharePoint module has been reset
- ADI scan is erroring

[Resolution]
- AIC resecured to port 481 (Ticket #00415743)
- Published Reports just needed the Netwrix Web Server service restarted after they rebound to port 443
- SharePoint configuration restored from archive (Ticket #00415745)
- ADI appeared to have a network hiccup, all looks good now and scan is running successfully
